Marta Fran Kauffman -LRB- born September 21 , 1956 -RRB- is an American writer and TV producer , best known as the co-creator of the popular sitcom Friends , alongside David Crane .
Both Kauffman and Crane were also executive producers of the show , along with Kevin Bright .
Kauffman and Crane also produced Veronica 's Closet , starring Kirstie Alley , and Jesse , starring Christina Applegate .
From 2005 -- 2006 she was an executive producer on Related .
Both writers were the creators of the 1990 HBO series Dream On .